    <h1>Globipedi Foundation Projects Privacy and Cookie Policy</h1>

    <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> February 2, 2024</p>

    <p>Welcome! This policy covers all projects provided by Globipedi Foundation and reflects our commitment to protecting user privacy.</p>

    <h2>1. Privacy and Collected Information:</h2>

    <p>Globipedi Foundation projects collect specific information only to improve the user experience and enhance our projects. This may include:</p>

    <ul>
        <li>User preferences and settings provided by the user.</li>
        <li>Browser and device information.</li>
        <li>Usage statistics and activities.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>This information is used to ensure the basic functionality of our projects, customize user experiences, and enhance security.</p>

    <h2>2. Use of Cookies:</h2>

    <p>Globipedi Foundation projects use cookies to improve and customize the user experience. For more information on cookie usage, please refer to our detailed <a href="#cookie-policy">Cookie Policy</a> section.</p>

    <h2>3. Types of Cookies Used:</h2>

    <ul>
        <li><strong>Essential Cookies:</strong> Necessary for basic functionality and remembering user preferences.</li>
        <li><strong>Analysis and Performance Cookies:</strong> Used to track visitor traffic, understand page popularity, and evaluate project performance.</li>
        <li><strong>Advertisement Cookies:</strong> Used to deliver targeted advertisements and measure the effectiveness of our advertising campaigns.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. Controlling Cookies:</h2>

    <p>You can control cookies through your browser settings. You have the option to disable cookies or permit them for specific websites.</p>

    <h2>5. Security and Privacy:</h2>

    <p>Globipedi Foundation securely stores collected information and never shares it with third parties. We prioritize user privacy protection.</p>

    <h2>6. Policy Updates:</h2>

    <p>This policy may be updated periodically. Users will be notified of significant changes.</p>

    <h2>7. Contact:</h2>

    <p>If you have questions or feedback regarding our privacy and cookie policy, please contact us through our <a href="#contact-information">Contact Information</a> section.</p>

    <p>This policy is applicable to all projects provided by Globipedi Foundation.</p>

